name: NodeSchool Denton
body:
### Node.js - Web programming re-imagined

Node.js offers the ability to express web applications in ways that Java and PHP can't.

NodeSchool Denton is a chapter of the international [NodeSchool.io](http://nodeschool.io/), and creates a container for learning Node.js, JavaScript, and web programming.
